WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
â™ªThat dayâ™ª

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
â™ªNothing stays together foreverâ™ª

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
â™ªI've quit romanceâ™ª

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
â™ªWho hasn't failed againâ™ª

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
â™ªCrying in deathâ™ª

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
â™ªAnd in lifeâ™ª

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
â™ªEven nowâ™ª

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
â™ªWe keep learningâ™ª

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
â™ªIt's no surpriseâ™ª

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
â™ªBeing happy is so hardâ™ª

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
â™ªWeirdly, I became a role modelâ™ª

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
â™ªOn the day we met again, we said hiâ™ª

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
â™ªIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaintâ™ª

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
â™ªWho can do anything without regretâ™ª

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
â™ªI am all rightâ™ª

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
â™ªMay you live in peaceâ™ª

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
â™ªLet the world roarâ™ª

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
â™ªSounds like a carnivalâ™ª

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
â™ªBeing alive is never dullâ™ª

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
â™ªHow wonderful to be freeâ™ª

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
â™ªI became even better without youâ™ª

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
â™ªNothing can be perfectâ™ª

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
â™ªWe bless each other in painâ™ª

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
â™ªWe nod and smileâ™ª

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
â™ªMay we both be wellâ™ª

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:43.801
=Episode 10=

01:44.195 --> 01:45.074
(Orthopedics Clinic 1)
My arm

01:45.115 --> 01:46.154
is completely healed.

01:46.555 --> 01:48.555
It's even more flexible than before.

01:48.555 --> 01:49.755
- Look.
- Enough.

01:50.154 --> 01:51.074
Be careful

01:51.395 --> 01:53.635
not to lift anything heavy
for three months.

01:53.714 --> 01:55.714
- Got it.
- Or you'll risk habitual dislocation.

01:55.755 --> 01:56.995
- Okay.
- Yiming.

01:57.434 --> 01:58.354
Let's go for food.

01:58.675 --> 01:59.635
Okay, go ahead.

02:04.555 --> 02:06.154
It's already mealtime.

02:06.354 --> 02:08.034
- Will you...?
- Okay, let's eat.

02:09.754 --> 02:10.995
I heard your canteen

02:11.034 --> 02:11.914
has great food.

02:12.275 --> 02:13.275
Alright, let's go.

02:19.474 --> 02:21.034
Wenjin, over here.

02:21.634 --> 02:22.474
Come sit with us.

02:23.634 --> 02:24.275
Come on.

02:26.154 --> 02:27.275
You don't know her, right?

02:27.835 --> 02:28.675
- Alright.
- Thanks.

02:28.714 --> 02:29.754
Let me introduce you.

02:30.675 --> 02:32.675
Yu Yiming, your senior.

02:33.555 --> 02:35.474
An orthopedic PhD two years above you.

02:36.275 --> 02:37.555
- Hello, senior.
- Hi.

02:37.914 --> 02:39.275
Xu Wenjin, your junior.

02:39.594 --> 02:40.714
Neurosurgery PhD.

02:41.474 --> 02:42.795
Top scorer in Shandong.

02:44.115 --> 02:45.515
Impressive. Nice to meet you.

02:46.075 --> 02:46.634
Me too.

02:47.955 --> 02:50.555
Guo, stop bringing up ancient history.

02:51.395 --> 02:52.275
Don't be modest.

02:52.634 --> 02:53.355
Right after

02:53.754 --> 02:54.714
her graduation,

02:54.835 --> 02:57.835
Wenjin got invited by
Memorial Sloan Kettering Cancer Center

02:57.955 --> 02:59.795
to a three-year cancer research project.

02:59.955 --> 03:00.835
I'm so jealous.

03:03.555 --> 03:05.594
Dig in. Should I get you some soup?

03:05.634 --> 03:06.795
No need, this is enough.

03:07.395 --> 03:08.600
Which department are you from?

03:08.835 --> 03:09.874
I'm not staff here.

03:10.395 --> 03:12.075
She's my high school classmate Qiao Lin.

03:12.235 --> 03:13.355
She happened to

03:13.555 --> 03:14.594
get my appointment

03:14.594 --> 03:15.952
- by chance.
- What a coincidence.

03:16.555 --> 03:17.634
What do you do?

03:18.194 --> 03:19.555
I sell cosmetics at a mall.

03:21.275 --> 03:22.995
She just came to Jingzhou alone.

03:23.115 --> 03:24.395
She's gaining experience

03:24.874 --> 03:25.555
for her career.

03:27.675 --> 03:28.874
I like makeup, too.

03:29.075 --> 03:30.034
But I think

03:30.075 --> 03:32.555
makeup requires skill just like surgery.

03:32.835 --> 03:33.955
Every morning, I try

03:33.955 --> 03:35.154
to learn from tutorial videos,

03:35.154 --> 03:36.176
but I never get it right.

03:38.675 --> 03:40.075
Why don't you visit my store?

03:40.835 --> 03:42.914
- I can do your makeup.
- Sounds great.

03:42.955 --> 03:45.034
I'll customize makeup based on

03:45.034 --> 03:46.115
your skin type and tone,

03:46.194 --> 03:48.034
and your facial features.

03:48.154 --> 03:50.034
Let me add you on WeChat.

03:50.115 --> 03:51.474
Come find me at the store.

03:51.555 --> 03:52.235
Alright.

03:53.555 --> 03:55.634
- Shall we do the same?
- Sure.

03:55.754 --> 03:56.154
Okay.

03:56.555 --> 03:57.115
I'll add you.

03:57.154 --> 03:57.594
Alright.

03:58.075 --> 03:59.795
Senior, let me add you too.

04:00.154 --> 04:00.555
Okay.

04:01.474 --> 04:02.474
Qiao Lin.

04:03.034 --> 04:03.874
I sent the request.

04:04.914 --> 04:05.434
Okay.

04:06.194 --> 04:06.634
Thanks.

04:08.675 --> 04:09.194
Dig in.

04:09.355 --> 04:09.795
Alright.

04:40.579 --> 04:43.760
(Conan)

05:43.355 --> 05:45.675
Do you want to watch TV

05:45.754 --> 05:46.995
or play games?

05:47.235 --> 05:47.995
Play games.

05:48.274 --> 05:49.274
Alright,

05:50.314 --> 05:52.035
but only thirty minutes.

05:52.035 --> 05:53.074
- Deal?
- Deal.

05:53.754 --> 05:54.194
Okay.

05:56.954 --> 05:58.394
Let me show you something first.

05:59.634 --> 06:00.235
Look.

06:03.995 --> 06:04.555
See?

06:07.874 --> 06:09.274
You took these?

06:11.811 --> 06:13.754
(Junlong Equestrian)

06:13.754 --> 06:14.995
You look really cool

06:14.995 --> 06:16.274
when riding,

06:17.074 --> 06:18.715
especially when you jump obstacles.

06:19.874 --> 06:22.115
You look almost like Hua Tian.

06:22.954 --> 06:24.274
You know Hua Tian?

06:24.475 --> 06:25.475
Of course, I do.

06:25.874 --> 06:28.675
He's your favorite equestrian athlete.

06:29.555 --> 06:31.035
He won

06:31.115 --> 06:33.115
the individual champion in show jumping

06:33.155 --> 06:34.274
and the team champion

06:34.314 --> 06:35.715
in the event.

06:37.274 --> 06:37.954
Listen.

06:38.274 --> 06:39.314
You can ask the coach

06:39.314 --> 06:40.155
to record videos

06:40.235 --> 06:41.874
during your future training.

06:42.035 --> 06:42.834
Then, you'll know

06:42.834 --> 06:43.834
your weaknesses

06:43.995 --> 06:45.795
and exactly what to work on.

06:50.355 --> 06:51.035
Look carefully.

06:51.634 --> 06:53.074
Then you can play games.

06:53.555 --> 06:54.795
I'll keep taking photos.

06:54.915 --> 06:55.394
Okay.

06:59.595 --> 07:00.434
Look at this move.

07:01.715 --> 07:02.355
Cool, huh?

07:02.595 --> 07:03.475
Check out the horse.

07:04.194 --> 07:05.595
What about the horse?

07:09.635 --> 07:11.536
(Hospital)

07:16.274 --> 07:16.754
How is he?

07:18.035 --> 07:19.754
He fell asleep after the IV.

07:31.675 --> 07:32.555
Are you working?

07:35.434 --> 07:36.834
I need to tell you something

07:36.834 --> 07:37.634
important.

07:38.915 --> 07:40.514
I didn't want to worry

07:40.514 --> 07:41.675
your parents.

07:45.675 --> 07:46.736
But Haochen

07:49.392 --> 07:51.155
fell from the horse on purpose.

07:52.355 --> 07:53.235
What do you mean?

08:07.475 --> 08:08.634
Why would he do that?

08:09.475 --> 08:10.434
I think

08:11.595 --> 08:13.555
he was trying to seek attention

08:14.954 --> 08:16.715
from his family.

08:18.754 --> 08:20.274
I've been observing Haochen.

08:20.555 --> 08:21.715
Whenever he's with

08:21.754 --> 08:22.954
you or your parents,

08:23.555 --> 08:25.475
he's extremely happy.

08:26.434 --> 08:27.434
But when you're gone,

08:27.434 --> 08:28.915
he gets very upset.

08:32.995 --> 08:35.914
But he shouldn't hurt himself.

08:36.754 --> 08:37.874
How would a child know

08:37.874 --> 08:39.554
the right way to cope?

08:43.835 --> 08:45.115
I have a friend.

08:50.715 --> 08:52.475
She told me that

08:52.554 --> 08:54.235
due to family hardships,

08:55.554 --> 08:57.034
she was sent away

08:57.995 --> 08:58.835
for foster care

08:58.835 --> 09:00.075
when she was young.

09:00.955 --> 09:02.914
Though they brought her home later,

09:05.435 --> 09:07.274
she still struggled to get

09:08.874 --> 09:10.674
the love and companionship she needed.

09:17.435 --> 09:18.274
What's wrong?

09:20.394 --> 09:21.754
Dad, Mom.

09:22.274 --> 09:22.715
What?

09:22.715 --> 09:23.394
Come here.

09:23.634 --> 09:24.195
My hand.

09:25.274 --> 09:25.914
You're hurt?

09:25.955 --> 09:26.914
Get a Band-Aid.

09:26.995 --> 09:27.634
Band-Aid.

09:28.554 --> 09:29.195
Come on.

09:29.394 --> 09:30.274
Right here.

09:30.274 --> 09:30.794
Put it on.

09:31.595 --> 09:32.874
Careful.

09:32.995 --> 09:34.235
Careful.

09:34.394 --> 09:35.715
Any other injuries?

09:36.315 --> 09:36.955
Anywhere else?

09:36.995 --> 09:38.075
Do your legs hurt?

09:38.235 --> 09:39.195
Easy now.

09:39.274 --> 09:39.835
Sweetheart.

09:40.235 --> 09:40.914
Take it slow.

09:46.754 --> 09:47.955
They say

09:49.754 --> 09:51.394
a happy childhood

09:52.235 --> 09:53.595
can heal you for a lifetime.

09:55.715 --> 09:57.075
But an unhappy one

10:00.235 --> 10:01.595
takes a lifetime to heal.

10:08.435 --> 10:09.514
That's why I believe

10:10.554 --> 10:12.355
no material comforts

10:13.674 --> 10:15.955
can replace family love and presence.

10:17.154 --> 10:17.754
Right?

10:22.235 --> 10:23.554
Haochen's too young.

10:25.674 --> 10:26.754
Can't we ask

10:27.034 --> 10:28.514
your parents to reconsider

10:29.075 --> 10:30.715
sending him abroad?

10:33.115 --> 10:35.315
Okay, let's do as you say.

10:37.955 --> 10:39.514
Thank you for caring for him.

10:40.554 --> 10:42.355
I'll go to the office early tomorrow

10:42.514 --> 10:43.674
and get the work done.

10:44.355 --> 10:46.674
Let's spend more time with him.

10:50.835 --> 10:51.435
Alright.

10:52.315 --> 10:53.514
Stay here with Haochen.

10:53.874 --> 10:55.355
I'll fetch some clothes.

10:55.475 --> 10:56.754
Okay, go ahead.

10:58.315 --> 10:59.274
I'll head back now.

11:00.274 --> 11:00.794
Bye.

11:18.674 --> 11:20.514
Qiao Lin, you're up next.

11:20.874 --> 11:21.274
Alright.

11:21.715 --> 11:23.115
Your sales performance is good.

11:24.075 --> 11:26.914
You achieved
the top regional ranking so soon.

11:27.034 --> 11:28.955
It's remarkable.

11:29.634 --> 11:31.154
Plus, the neo-Chinese-style makeup

11:31.154 --> 11:32.195
you did for clients

11:32.394 --> 11:33.514
went viral online

11:33.754 --> 11:35.794
with great reviews.

11:36.154 --> 11:38.034
It benefits our brand image.

11:38.394 --> 11:40.435
We're promoting a salesperson

11:40.435 --> 11:42.715
from the store to the headquarters'

11:42.715 --> 11:43.955
sales team.

11:44.075 --> 11:45.674
You're on the shortlist.

11:48.115 --> 11:49.674
Thank you for the recognition.

11:49.874 --> 11:52.034
I genuinely love this industry,

11:52.195 --> 11:53.235
especially when

11:53.274 --> 11:54.955
the customers like the makeup I've done.

11:55.034 --> 11:56.034
Their happiness

11:56.115 --> 11:57.835
makes me happy too.

11:58.715 --> 12:00.794
Who do you think
should get the last spot?

12:01.235 --> 12:02.955
Qiao Lin might be alright.

12:03.914 --> 12:04.794
Qiao Lin.

12:05.195 --> 12:06.315
That girl's decent.

12:06.914 --> 12:08.514
But her education level is too low.

12:09.514 --> 12:10.394
What a shame.

12:10.794 --> 12:12.355
Let's stick to the standards.

12:12.674 --> 12:13.154
Alright.

12:16.715 --> 12:17.554
Education level.

12:20.483 --> 12:23.120
(Interview result: Failed)

12:25.955 --> 12:28.835
What's wrong? Did you get eliminated?

12:31.315 --> 12:32.154
You know what?

12:32.195 --> 12:33.235
This industry keeps

12:33.355 --> 12:34.634
getting more competitive.

12:35.154 --> 12:36.355
My cousin graduated

12:36.715 --> 12:38.514
from a world-renowned university,

12:39.195 --> 12:40.754
but started as a sales associate.

12:40.914 --> 12:42.034
So forget about it.

12:54.475 --> 12:55.634
You've already ordered?

12:55.955 --> 12:56.315
Well,

12:56.315 --> 12:57.715
I invited you for food,

12:57.715 --> 12:58.514
but I'm late.

12:58.794 --> 12:59.674
Sorry.

12:59.914 --> 13:00.394
No worries.

13:00.634 --> 13:01.195
Let's eat.

13:01.394 --> 13:01.914
Okay.

13:02.914 --> 13:04.075
You bought a new laptop?

13:06.634 --> 13:07.634
It's for work?

13:08.075 --> 13:09.274
The trends are changing

13:09.274 --> 13:10.154
way too fast.

13:10.394 --> 13:12.355
I bought it to study

13:13.034 --> 13:13.835
and gather

13:13.835 --> 13:14.955
information on

13:14.955 --> 13:16.034
the latest makeup styles.

13:17.794 --> 13:19.754
Plus, I want to continue my education.

13:20.394 --> 13:22.034
I want to enroll in adult education

13:22.075 --> 13:23.355
to improve my qualifications.

13:25.394 --> 13:26.115
Sounds great.

13:26.874 --> 13:27.475
I fully

13:27.475 --> 13:28.355
support you.

13:29.034 --> 13:30.394
Don't rush to say that.

13:31.075 --> 13:32.034
I'm just having

13:32.034 --> 13:32.874
this idea.

13:33.115 --> 13:35.034
But I haven't decided on a major

13:35.034 --> 13:36.034
or anything.

13:36.195 --> 13:37.034
That's why I wanted

13:37.034 --> 13:38.115
to talk with you.

13:38.674 --> 13:39.195
Alright,

13:40.195 --> 13:41.075
tell me.

13:41.514 --> 13:42.595
What's on your mind?

13:43.195 --> 13:44.034
Well, currently,

13:44.115 --> 13:45.595
I'm just doing sales.

13:45.595 --> 13:47.075
A relevant major

13:47.075 --> 13:49.034
would be marketing.

13:49.235 --> 13:50.754
I want to join adult education.

13:51.154 --> 13:52.634
It's not so easy to graduate

13:53.794 --> 13:55.235
from those programs.

13:55.715 --> 13:56.955
So I was thinking,

13:57.235 --> 13:59.274
even if I choose a major I like,

13:59.435 --> 14:01.034
the courses I'm weak in

14:01.034 --> 14:02.195
could still become

14:02.195 --> 14:03.195
obstacles, right?

14:03.595 --> 14:04.634
That's why I thought

14:04.634 --> 14:05.674
that maybe

14:06.195 --> 14:07.794
you could tutor me in math

14:07.794 --> 14:08.794
and help me catch up.

14:10.034 --> 14:11.514
Please don't say no.

14:11.514 --> 14:12.475
Please please.

14:12.595 --> 14:14.274
No one else will help me but you.

14:15.634 --> 14:17.355
I'm begging you.

14:17.355 --> 14:18.274
I'm begging you.

14:21.634 --> 14:22.674
- Please.
- Alright.

14:22.914 --> 14:23.955
But I might not

14:24.835 --> 14:25.794
be a good teacher.

14:25.955 --> 14:26.914
You'll be the best.

14:27.034 --> 14:27.874
Mr. Yu, cheers.

14:31.075 --> 14:33.424
(Jingzhou Yuekang Hospital)

14:38.034 --> 14:39.274
Have some breakfast.

14:40.154 --> 14:41.195
Your brother will come

14:41.554 --> 14:42.914
after the meeting.

14:43.435 --> 14:44.154
He promised.

14:45.075 --> 14:46.835
And he visited last night.

14:47.955 --> 14:49.634
He bought you this. You like it, huh?

14:52.475 --> 14:53.235
Play later.

14:56.034 --> 14:57.394
Thank you, sis-in-law.

14:58.634 --> 14:59.634
You're welcome.

15:15.235 --> 15:15.835
Did...

15:18.514 --> 15:19.435
Did you just

15:20.475 --> 15:22.554
call me "sis-in-law"?

15:26.595 --> 15:27.394
Sis-in-law.

15:29.674 --> 15:30.394
Well,

15:30.754 --> 15:32.195
I was rude yesterday.

15:33.235 --> 15:34.075
Sorry about that.

15:42.794 --> 15:44.554
Good kid for admitting mistakes.

15:45.435 --> 15:46.355
You're forgiven.

15:46.674 --> 15:47.754
Sis-in-law forgives you.

15:54.794 --> 15:55.595
Want some soy milk?

15:58.674 --> 15:59.394
I-I'll do it.

16:03.355 --> 16:03.874
Wipe it.

16:05.914 --> 16:06.514
Hands.

16:14.355 --> 16:14.914
Sis-in-law.

16:16.634 --> 16:19.634
You said you could
keep me from going abroad.

16:20.034 --> 16:20.955
Is that true?

16:22.475 --> 16:23.554
Of course, it's true.

16:23.835 --> 16:24.674
Would I lie to you?

16:25.195 --> 16:27.274
But you must listen to me.

16:28.754 --> 16:29.235
Okay.

16:30.595 --> 16:31.475
Have an egg.

16:35.995 --> 16:36.715
What's wrong?

16:41.235 --> 16:41.674
Here.

16:56.075 --> 16:57.394
I've brought you the iPad.

16:57.794 --> 16:59.355
And I renewed your membership.

17:01.075 --> 17:01.674
Let's go.

17:02.514 --> 17:03.274
Rest your eyes.

17:03.595 --> 17:04.834
Protect your eyesight.

17:05.274 --> 17:06.915
Call me if you need anything.

17:06.915 --> 17:08.314
Yeah, we're leaving.

17:08.314 --> 17:09.514
- Dad...
- Yan, take care of him.

17:09.514 --> 17:10.554
- Dad...
- Call us.

17:10.554 --> 17:11.715
Mom, Dad.

17:11.955 --> 17:13.875
Wait a minute.

17:19.395 --> 17:21.354
What's wrong? Do you need something?

17:22.754 --> 17:25.235
Can you stay with Haochen today?

17:25.354 --> 17:26.195
We have meetings.

17:27.314 --> 17:28.834
But Haochen is getting

17:28.834 --> 17:30.235
even more upset.

17:30.314 --> 17:31.475
We must take it seriously.

17:31.834 --> 17:32.955
Yeah, I've noticed.

17:33.034 --> 17:34.475
We're making time to visit him.

17:34.715 --> 17:36.554
We brought his iPad, but that kid barely

17:36.554 --> 17:37.155
speaks to us.

17:37.155 --> 17:38.074
Kids are rebellious

17:38.074 --> 17:39.475
- during puberty.
- Yeah.

17:41.114 --> 17:41.794
Take a look

17:41.794 --> 17:42.754
at Haochen's drawing.

17:45.715 --> 17:47.514
- What's this?
- My Mom and Dad.

17:47.635 --> 17:48.754
(My Mom and Dad)
Well done.

17:49.034 --> 17:50.435
Our heads are smartphones.

17:50.915 --> 17:53.235
Our child has remarkable creativity.

17:53.354 --> 17:55.475
I'd give him five stars
if I were his art teacher.

17:55.475 --> 17:57.754
This is what Haochen thinks of you.

17:58.074 --> 18:00.114
This is Haochen

18:00.114 --> 18:01.114
when he's alone.

18:02.155 --> 18:02.834
Is this healthy?

18:07.235 --> 18:08.915
He has always lacked companionship.

18:09.955 --> 18:11.875
The person who spent
the most time with him

18:11.875 --> 18:12.915
was the nanny.

18:15.195 --> 18:16.915
You're busy. Haoming's busy.

18:17.594 --> 18:18.915
You spent more time

18:18.915 --> 18:20.915
on your phones than with Haochen.

18:21.834 --> 18:23.834
He does have many years ahead of him.

18:25.554 --> 18:26.715
But childhood is short.

18:27.635 --> 18:28.594
Haochen doesn't really

18:28.675 --> 18:30.554
want his iPad or smartphone.

18:31.114 --> 18:32.554
He wants what's most precious

18:32.554 --> 18:33.594
to you.

18:34.754 --> 18:35.554
Your time.

18:46.794 --> 18:48.554
So I'm asking you to stay

18:50.314 --> 18:53.195
and keep him company

18:55.675 --> 18:56.435
for just one day.

19:01.635 --> 19:03.754
Mom, Dad, Haochen, food is ready.

19:04.274 --> 19:04.875
Go ahead.

19:05.554 --> 19:06.354
Yeah, go ahead.

19:06.435 --> 19:07.554
We're watching the match.

19:09.235 --> 19:10.794
A pity, huh?

19:12.114 --> 19:13.034
One question for you.

19:14.435 --> 19:16.155
Why did I make you learn equestrian?

19:20.475 --> 19:21.155
You know what?

19:22.114 --> 19:23.955
I've chosen an excellent school for you.

19:24.314 --> 19:26.475
This school offers eleven sports.

19:26.475 --> 19:28.395
Equestrian ranks first.

19:28.395 --> 19:30.435
Equestrian is a graceful sport.

19:30.754 --> 19:32.104
If you master equestrian skills

19:32.104 --> 19:33.475
before entering this school,

19:33.475 --> 19:35.114
you've already gained an advantage.

19:37.675 --> 19:38.155
Have it.

19:45.034 --> 19:45.715
Thank you.

20:22.675 --> 20:24.395
I won't drive you back today.

20:26.034 --> 20:26.514
Okay.

20:28.995 --> 20:30.155
It's red, your favorite.

20:30.834 --> 20:31.435
It's for you.

20:32.514 --> 20:33.354
Why?

20:34.554 --> 20:35.594
To congratulate you.

20:36.034 --> 20:39.514
Your financial news broadcasts
have been so well-received this week.

20:40.314 --> 20:41.554
Given your current status,

20:42.074 --> 20:43.675
having a car makes a statement.

20:44.195 --> 20:44.915
Also,

20:45.715 --> 20:47.114
Haochen has been spoiled

20:47.554 --> 20:48.875
ever since he was born.

20:49.235 --> 20:50.114
His temper

20:50.114 --> 20:51.195
grew worse and worse.

20:51.554 --> 20:53.195
Even the formidable Ms. Yu

20:53.514 --> 20:54.395
couldn't handle him.

20:55.155 --> 20:56.235
I never expected

20:57.155 --> 20:58.675
you'd get along so well with him.

20:59.435 --> 21:00.594
I can sense that

21:00.635 --> 21:02.314
he genuinely likes you.

21:02.715 --> 21:04.155
And he got badly injured.

21:04.794 --> 21:06.114
He's been discharged early

21:06.554 --> 21:07.754
thanks to you.

21:09.034 --> 21:10.314
Haochen is your brother.

21:10.395 --> 21:11.675
We're family.

21:11.955 --> 21:13.314
It's only natural for us

21:13.314 --> 21:14.675
to care for each other.

21:14.754 --> 21:16.034
You don't have to buy me gifts

21:16.034 --> 21:17.594
whenever I do something.

21:17.594 --> 21:18.794
You've done a great job.

21:19.834 --> 21:21.114
You deserve a reward.

21:21.955 --> 21:23.554
Because I appreciate it.

21:24.594 --> 21:25.915
You're a typical boss.

21:26.554 --> 21:27.675
Your expression of emotions

21:27.675 --> 21:28.794
has become transactional.

21:29.715 --> 21:30.754
I just want to give you

21:31.314 --> 21:32.514
the life you want.

21:34.514 --> 21:36.235
You are all I want.

21:44.594 --> 21:45.314
See you.

21:59.794 --> 22:00.435
(Zhou Zeyuan)
(Let's meet.)

22:09.195 --> 22:10.314
These are my company's

22:10.314 --> 22:11.514
financial reports.

22:12.794 --> 22:14.754
Here are the ongoing

22:14.754 --> 22:15.514
(Projects)
R&D Projects.

22:16.635 --> 22:18.435
Here's the project proposal.

22:19.195 --> 22:19.834
All here.

22:32.754 --> 22:33.594
I came to tell you

22:33.594 --> 22:34.715
that your collaboration

22:36.675 --> 22:37.915
with my husband

22:37.955 --> 22:38.915
won't happen.

22:43.354 --> 22:43.995
Why not?

22:44.274 --> 22:45.435
I work in journalism

22:45.794 --> 22:47.395
and conduct investigations.

22:47.955 --> 22:49.074
All your employees here

22:49.114 --> 22:50.395
are hired actors.

22:51.794 --> 22:54.034
This whole company is just a front

22:54.995 --> 22:57.395
to scam money from investors.

22:58.034 --> 22:59.034
So I'm sure

22:59.915 --> 23:01.995
you don't have any real operations.

23:06.635 --> 23:08.715
I'm not surprised

23:08.715 --> 23:11.955
you saw through this.
You know better about

23:12.354 --> 23:13.314
hiring actors.

23:20.195 --> 23:20.955
What do you mean?

23:21.395 --> 23:23.955
Your parents aren't actually abroad.

23:24.314 --> 23:25.955
They live in a small town.

23:27.074 --> 23:27.955
When they came

23:27.955 --> 23:29.155
to visit you in Jingzhou,

23:29.155 --> 23:30.195
you treated them coldly.

23:30.235 --> 23:31.195
They left quickly.

23:31.635 --> 23:33.594
I met them briefly then.

23:33.794 --> 23:34.875
I don't have many strengths

23:34.875 --> 23:36.274
except a good memory.

23:39.314 --> 23:40.715
Don't bother forming

23:40.715 --> 23:41.594
a strategy.

23:41.834 --> 23:43.114
I never intended

23:43.114 --> 23:44.114
to destroy

23:44.114 --> 23:45.794
what you've achieved.

23:46.195 --> 23:47.554
My company needs funding.

23:47.554 --> 23:48.915
You married into wealth.

23:49.034 --> 23:49.834
Helping me

23:50.074 --> 23:52.114
would be effortless for you.

24:04.034 --> 24:04.635
Zeyuan,

24:05.554 --> 24:06.514
I still remember

24:06.834 --> 24:07.875
that you told me

24:07.915 --> 24:09.834
to be honest on resumes

24:11.195 --> 24:11.875
and that I must

24:12.794 --> 24:13.955
walk in the light.

24:16.875 --> 24:18.395
So I don't understand

24:19.235 --> 24:20.314
why you've become

24:20.314 --> 24:21.314
like this now.

24:22.435 --> 24:23.594
Then why did you hide

24:23.594 --> 24:25.034
your family background?

24:26.155 --> 24:27.034
Why would you

24:27.034 --> 24:28.195
hide your real parents

24:28.195 --> 24:29.274
in the dark?

24:29.395 --> 24:30.435
I saw your wedding photo

24:30.514 --> 24:31.635
at Ms. Ma's place.

24:31.675 --> 24:33.034
Those fake parents of yours

24:34.114 --> 24:35.995
do look like educated elites.

24:36.354 --> 24:37.195
But I get it.

24:37.675 --> 24:39.514
Without these glamorous facades,

24:39.514 --> 24:41.195
every step we take would be harder.

24:41.715 --> 24:42.635
We've both struggled.

24:43.435 --> 24:44.715
I bet you know this.

24:44.715 --> 24:45.675
No matter how hard

24:45.675 --> 24:46.834
you try, some things

24:46.834 --> 24:47.675
don't change.

24:47.955 --> 24:49.514
Those of us who come from nothing

24:49.514 --> 24:50.754
need to dress ourselves

24:50.754 --> 24:51.675
in noble disguises.

24:58.195 --> 24:59.514
Since we're the same,

25:00.514 --> 25:02.235
let's help each other.

25:27.114 --> 25:27.635
Yan.

25:31.155 --> 25:32.034
You're finally back.

25:32.314 --> 25:33.074
What's wrong, Mom?

25:33.314 --> 25:35.314
Haochen's birthday is early next month.

25:35.314 --> 25:36.875
How should we celebrate it?

25:37.955 --> 25:39.155
You can decide.

25:39.554 --> 25:41.395
I asked him, but he wouldn't talk.

25:41.475 --> 25:42.754
I can't handle this kid.

25:42.955 --> 25:45.235
He likes you. He'll like
whatever you do for him.

25:48.114 --> 25:48.794
Let me think.

25:49.915 --> 25:52.715
Ms. Ma is bringing a friend tomorrow.

25:53.034 --> 25:53.995
She's so picky.

25:54.034 --> 25:54.875
I have no idea

25:54.875 --> 25:56.435
what to cook for her.

25:56.834 --> 25:57.435
Help me.

25:59.594 --> 26:01.155
Ms. Ma likes shrimp.

26:01.475 --> 26:02.754
Maybe I'll make her

26:02.875 --> 26:04.314
shrimp with black truffle oil.

26:04.955 --> 26:05.514
- How's that?
- Perfect.

26:05.675 --> 26:06.875
And she's dieting.

26:07.395 --> 26:08.875
I'll keep the dishes low-calorie.

26:08.875 --> 26:09.514
Rest assured.

26:09.794 --> 26:11.435
I know I can count on you.

26:12.514 --> 26:14.354
Hui said she needs you in the kitchen.

26:15.235 --> 26:16.514
- I'll go then.
- Go ahead.

26:21.915 --> 26:23.435
- What's wrong, Hui?
- Yan.

26:23.995 --> 26:25.955
How should I cook these tonight?

26:27.995 --> 26:29.395
Steam the rainbow trout.

26:29.514 --> 26:30.754
Haochen has been coughing.

26:31.034 --> 26:32.875
Skip the seafood. It's inflammatory.

26:32.955 --> 26:34.875
Replace them with vegetarian dishes.

26:35.235 --> 26:35.635
Okay.

26:36.475 --> 26:38.594
Did the fruits I ordered arrive?

26:39.114 --> 26:40.554
I washed and refrigerated them.

26:40.594 --> 26:42.074
Alright, I'm heading back then.

26:42.235 --> 26:42.834
Yan.

26:45.074 --> 26:46.594
I may need a day off tomorrow

26:46.875 --> 26:48.235
for personal matters.

26:49.074 --> 26:51.875
But Ms. Yu needs help
hosting guests tomorrow.

26:51.875 --> 26:53.114
Go ahead. I'll handle it.

26:54.195 --> 26:54.754
Really?

26:55.995 --> 26:57.794
With you here, I'm completely at ease.

26:58.074 --> 27:00.195
They all love your cooking.

27:01.955 --> 27:03.395
Only because you help me.

27:05.915 --> 27:06.554
Yan.

27:07.875 --> 27:08.955
You seem

27:08.955 --> 27:10.274
different from before.

27:12.915 --> 27:13.754
How so?

27:15.034 --> 27:15.955
Now, you look

27:16.195 --> 27:17.754
like the lady of the house.

27:19.363 --> 27:24.314
â™ªI was lost in the dark,
and it's too hurt to even seeâ™ª

27:24.314 --> 27:25.155
I'm leaving.

27:25.680 --> 27:31.061
â™ªSee the world and how it flows.
We never let goâ™ª

27:31.299 --> 27:32.794
(Jingzhou Yuekang Hospital)

27:32.794 --> 27:34.594
You want to take on patient No. 38's

27:34.594 --> 27:36.195
spine correction surgery?

27:36.554 --> 27:37.074
Yes, sir.

27:37.200 --> 27:40.235
Type 1 neurofibromatosis with scoliosis.

27:40.635 --> 27:42.715
This surgery requires extreme precision.

27:43.155 --> 27:46.435
Any mistake could cause
lifelong paralysis.

27:46.875 --> 27:48.475
And the patient's young.

27:48.915 --> 27:49.834
It's very challenging.

27:50.195 --> 27:50.995
I understand.

27:51.554 --> 27:52.514
My plan is to conduct

27:53.435 --> 27:54.435
multiple staged surgeries

27:55.034 --> 27:56.754
to minimize risks.

27:57.155 --> 27:57.675
Of course,

27:58.114 --> 27:58.995
we'll monitor

27:58.995 --> 28:01.235
the patient's tolerance responses

28:01.395 --> 28:02.475
during the operation.

28:03.155 --> 28:04.155
Of course, I know

28:04.235 --> 28:05.314
the family has concerns.

28:05.955 --> 28:07.834
We'll handle
pre-op communication carefully.

28:07.875 --> 28:08.354
Okay.

28:09.074 --> 28:10.235
Your suggestions are noted.

28:10.995 --> 28:14.195
I'll discuss with the higher-ups.

28:15.435 --> 28:15.915
Alright.

28:18.475 --> 28:19.314
Thank you, sir.

28:31.155 --> 28:32.354
This is a bit spicy.

28:32.514 --> 28:33.395
Not at all.

28:33.435 --> 28:34.395
It's amazing.

28:34.834 --> 28:35.195
Skewers.

28:35.635 --> 28:37.114
Have it while it's hot.

28:37.235 --> 28:38.715
Super crispy. That's why we came.

28:38.715 --> 28:39.074
Okay.

28:39.395 --> 28:40.514
Smells great.

28:42.314 --> 28:42.995
What's her deal?

28:50.114 --> 28:50.955
What's wrong?

28:51.875 --> 28:53.034
Why are you silent?

28:53.314 --> 28:54.834
You ordered this. Won't you eat?

28:55.274 --> 28:56.074
This is good.

28:58.395 --> 29:00.114
Dig in. Don't just watch me.

29:00.354 --> 29:01.834
I shouldn't. I'm on a diet.

29:02.114 --> 29:03.114
That's too much.

29:04.274 --> 29:05.955
I'll gain 500 grams tomorrow.

29:06.915 --> 29:08.314
Dig in. I'll be right back.

29:11.915 --> 29:12.594
Yu Yiming.

29:13.594 --> 29:14.475
You're alone?

29:15.195 --> 29:15.875
Why are you here?

29:16.395 --> 29:17.155
I came with my...

29:19.114 --> 29:21.475
I'm just getting some skewers to go.

29:24.635 --> 29:25.155
I...

29:26.395 --> 29:27.715
I've never seen you drink.

29:28.514 --> 29:29.995
I avoided drinking because of work.

29:30.915 --> 29:32.915
Fine. Let me join you.
Waiter. A dozen beers.

29:33.955 --> 29:35.314
Mind your head. Oh my.

29:44.155 --> 29:44.635
Here.

29:46.435 --> 29:47.514
Have some water.

30:46.554 --> 30:47.314
Well...

30:48.314 --> 30:49.354
I bought you breakfast.

30:59.875 --> 31:01.395
I overdrank because I was

31:02.074 --> 31:03.554
overwhelmed with the surgery.

31:06.074 --> 31:07.314
I do remember what happened

31:08.514 --> 31:09.395
afterward.

31:17.514 --> 31:19.475
You should have told me.

31:19.794 --> 31:20.514
Forget about it.

31:22.554 --> 31:23.754
N-Nothing happened.

31:24.314 --> 31:24.834
Right?

31:25.715 --> 31:27.074
You're pretty heavy, by the way.

31:27.074 --> 31:28.554
Carrying you was exhausting.

31:28.995 --> 31:30.514
Yeah, sorry about that.

31:31.635 --> 31:32.594
It won't happen again.

31:32.635 --> 31:33.675
It's fine. It can happen.

31:36.114 --> 31:36.955
No, no.

31:37.834 --> 31:38.834
That's not what I meant.

31:39.395 --> 31:41.114
You're under too much stress.

31:41.114 --> 31:42.354
Letting loose occasionally

31:42.354 --> 31:43.915
is actually good for you.

31:47.195 --> 31:48.195
This is good.

31:48.635 --> 31:48.995
Yeah.

31:49.328 --> 31:50.896
Have you spoken to your sister lately?

31:51.514 --> 31:52.114
No.

31:52.834 --> 31:54.155
She's happy that you're attending

31:54.314 --> 31:55.114
adult college.

31:58.155 --> 32:01.074
You've been updating her about me?

32:02.395 --> 32:03.875
She asked me to look after you.

32:05.715 --> 32:06.955
She could've told me herself.

32:09.195 --> 32:10.995
You're quite similar.

32:11.514 --> 32:12.235
Both stubborn.

32:12.834 --> 32:14.314
You care about each other,

32:14.955 --> 32:16.715
but can't sit down for a proper talk.

32:19.635 --> 32:22.395
I wish you could open up
to each other someday,

32:22.715 --> 32:23.888
without a messenger like me.

32:26.114 --> 32:27.195
It doesn't matter.

32:29.834 --> 32:30.514
Spin.

32:30.514 --> 32:31.314
Hide.

32:31.475 --> 32:32.114
Run.

32:32.834 --> 32:33.915
Can't find it.

32:33.915 --> 32:34.435
Nice.

32:34.594 --> 32:35.875
You ruined my dress.

32:36.274 --> 32:37.074
Bu. Sweetie.

32:37.074 --> 32:37.475
Fetch.

32:38.915 --> 32:39.435
Where is it?

32:40.114 --> 32:41.955
Ms. Yu is really nice.

32:43.794 --> 32:44.475
Well done.

32:45.514 --> 32:46.114
Come here.

32:46.354 --> 32:47.155
Ms. Yu.

32:48.514 --> 32:49.155
Tianzi.

32:49.354 --> 32:50.314
What took you so long?

32:52.715 --> 32:53.875
We've been waiting forever.

32:54.314 --> 32:55.240
I'm slow getting ready.

32:55.354 --> 32:57.314
Ms. Yu, meet my friend.

32:57.915 --> 32:59.354
Zhou Zeyuan, Mr. Zhou.

32:59.675 --> 33:01.034
He's a rising star in tech.

33:01.635 --> 33:02.915
- Hello, Ms. Yu.
- Hello.

33:03.034 --> 33:04.395
Ms. Ma speaks highly of you.

33:04.834 --> 33:05.794
Just call me Randy.

33:05.995 --> 33:06.514
Randy.

33:07.955 --> 33:08.875
This is

33:09.195 --> 33:11.354
Ms. Yu's daughter-in-law, Xu Yan.

33:12.034 --> 33:12.715
Ms. Ma.

33:13.274 --> 33:13.715
Hello.

33:13.995 --> 33:15.514
Hello, Miss Xu.

33:16.995 --> 33:17.675
Hello.

33:19.074 --> 33:20.114
Let's sit over there.

33:22.074 --> 33:23.034
I prepared

33:23.034 --> 33:23.995
your favorite tea.

33:24.235 --> 33:25.794
Thank you, Ms. Yu.

33:26.475 --> 33:28.235
No wonder you won't hang out with me.

33:28.314 --> 33:30.354
You prefer a younger company now.

33:31.635 --> 33:34.074
You know me best, Ms. Yu.

33:34.155 --> 33:35.274
I just love

33:35.635 --> 33:36.594
supporting

33:36.594 --> 33:37.754
young entrepreneurs.

33:38.395 --> 33:41.675
I met Randy at the venture forum,
and we hit it off.

33:42.034 --> 33:43.834
So I'm introducing him to you.

33:44.754 --> 33:47.155
Randy, what exactly do you do?

33:48.034 --> 33:48.475
Ms. Yu,

33:48.915 --> 33:50.314
I work in new medical tech.

33:50.794 --> 33:52.915
I empower medical systems

33:53.074 --> 33:53.995
with cutting-edge tech,

33:54.554 --> 33:56.034
making healthcare accessible

33:56.274 --> 33:57.915
and streamlining doctors' work.

33:58.635 --> 33:59.155
Ms. Yu,

33:59.514 --> 34:01.794
this is the hottest field now.

34:01.915 --> 34:03.395
Young people today

34:03.594 --> 34:04.635
have talent

34:04.794 --> 34:05.675
and drive.

34:05.915 --> 34:07.715
They just need resources and chances.

34:08.435 --> 34:09.714
Supporting them

34:09.795 --> 34:10.875
benefits us too.

34:10.995 --> 34:12.514
It's a win-win.

34:19.714 --> 34:20.275
Ms. Yu,

34:21.074 --> 34:22.594
if I'm not mistaken,

34:22.714 --> 34:24.234
your outfit is from

34:24.475 --> 34:25.714
that famous Italian designer,

34:25.714 --> 34:26.915
Maygeogin, right?

34:27.275 --> 34:30.315
Yeah, it's the new model
they just released this year.

34:30.594 --> 34:33.594
This designer debuted recently
and is still niche.

34:33.915 --> 34:35.234
Few people know about her.

34:36.395 --> 34:37.514
How could you tell?

34:38.475 --> 34:39.995
She held a fashion show in New York

34:40.034 --> 34:41.154
when she graduated

34:41.435 --> 34:42.435
from Parsons,

34:42.435 --> 34:43.514
and we met there.

34:43.875 --> 34:45.875
Her works have a strong and impressive

34:45.875 --> 34:46.955
personal style.

34:48.114 --> 34:50.275
I thought people in tech
and the internet industries

34:50.275 --> 34:52.114
weren't that interested in fashion.

34:52.594 --> 34:54.074
But you're a connoisseur.

34:56.714 --> 34:58.514
Mom, I'll get some hot water.

34:58.674 --> 34:59.755
- Excuse me.
- Okay.

34:59.755 --> 35:00.554
Take your time.

35:04.355 --> 35:05.435
You know, Ms. Yu.

35:05.875 --> 35:07.475
Randy mainly works on tech,

35:07.594 --> 35:09.634
but he has great connections.

35:09.634 --> 35:10.795
He has many friends from

35:10.795 --> 35:12.074
the fashion and art circles.

35:12.234 --> 35:14.194
His taste is impeccable.

35:19.154 --> 35:19.755
Miss Xu.

35:21.194 --> 35:22.674
Where's the restroom?

35:36.915 --> 35:38.514
Should I discuss with you

35:39.755 --> 35:41.234
or your mother-in-law

35:43.514 --> 35:44.674
about the investment?

35:45.634 --> 35:46.475
Zhou Zeyuan.

35:51.755 --> 35:52.475
Randy.

35:54.114 --> 35:55.234
You're being naive.

35:55.795 --> 35:57.154
Your business proposal

35:57.634 --> 35:58.795
and financial statements

35:59.194 --> 36:00.154
can't fool

36:00.154 --> 36:01.114
my mother-in-law

36:02.154 --> 36:03.275
or my husband.

36:04.674 --> 36:06.074
Forget about getting investment.

36:08.315 --> 36:09.835
Whether he invests

36:10.034 --> 36:11.395
depends on how well you whisper

36:11.395 --> 36:12.435
in his ear.

36:13.835 --> 36:17.074
Besides, I'm only asking for
a tiny investment from him.

36:17.275 --> 36:18.674
He won't care about it.

36:19.435 --> 36:20.114
What do you mean?

36:20.955 --> 36:21.875
In this circle,

36:22.114 --> 36:23.355
how much you get

36:23.554 --> 36:25.114
isn't as important as

36:25.114 --> 36:26.034
who you get it from.

36:26.435 --> 36:27.955
A hundred thousand from a tycoon

36:28.194 --> 36:29.594
is more valuable than

36:29.594 --> 36:31.674
five million from some island chief.

36:31.995 --> 36:33.755
For other investors,

36:33.995 --> 36:35.435
who back you up

36:35.435 --> 36:36.594
and endorse you,

36:36.755 --> 36:37.875
is their primary criterion

36:37.875 --> 36:39.714
to judge your potential.

36:40.315 --> 36:41.714
That's why I never intended

36:41.714 --> 36:42.714
to have your husband

36:42.795 --> 36:44.154
make big investments.

36:46.275 --> 36:47.634
You want to use his reputation

36:47.634 --> 36:49.475
to attract more money, right?

36:55.435 --> 36:56.714
It just hit me

36:57.755 --> 36:58.995
how incredibly attractive

37:01.435 --> 37:02.755
intelligent women look.

37:02.755 --> 37:03.755
You're disgusting.

37:04.674 --> 37:06.034
Let me make it clear.

37:06.995 --> 37:07.594
No.

37:08.835 --> 37:09.755
Xu Yan, you...

37:12.755 --> 37:13.514
Qiao Yan.

37:14.234 --> 37:16.234
This name makes us closer, doesn't it?

37:16.795 --> 37:17.995
Don't tell me that

37:18.154 --> 37:19.355
you genuinely

37:19.355 --> 37:20.594
love Shen Haoming,

37:20.634 --> 37:23.114
not his money, status,

37:23.275 --> 37:24.514
or his family's influence.

37:31.315 --> 37:32.795
I don't owe you explanations.

37:33.234 --> 37:34.275
But you should know

37:35.634 --> 37:36.835
everything you're doing now

37:36.835 --> 37:38.475
is extortion and illegal.

37:39.315 --> 37:39.995
Qiao Yan.

37:40.795 --> 37:42.995
It's fascinating how much you're trying

37:43.034 --> 37:44.114
to protect Shen Haoming.

37:44.355 --> 37:46.034
You're actually love-struck.

37:46.634 --> 37:48.435
Let me tell you
the most ridiculous story

37:48.514 --> 37:49.795
I've heard this year.

37:50.154 --> 37:51.955
A common scammer married into wealth

37:51.955 --> 37:52.875
not for money,

37:52.875 --> 37:54.475
but for true love.

37:54.795 --> 37:56.915
Isn't this more absurd
than fairy tales...?

38:07.594 --> 38:08.875
Thankfully, it's not burning.

38:11.234 --> 38:12.112
The dry-cleaning bill

38:13.475 --> 38:14.714
is included in the investment.

38:20.074 --> 38:21.034
So smart.

38:21.034 --> 38:22.395
Unbelievable.

38:22.395 --> 38:23.714
Ms. Yu, really,

38:24.034 --> 38:26.194
you've even trained Bu so well.

38:26.795 --> 38:28.275
You're amazing.

38:28.275 --> 38:29.355
I'm so clumsy.

38:29.755 --> 38:31.034
I splashed water everywhere

38:31.034 --> 38:32.275
when I washed my hands.

38:34.034 --> 38:35.315
You're hilarious.

38:35.395 --> 38:36.315
It's okay.

38:36.435 --> 38:37.594
I'll have Yan bring

38:37.594 --> 38:38.835
Haoming's clothes.

38:38.835 --> 38:39.955
You can wear those.

38:40.355 --> 38:42.435
- Sorry for the trouble.
- Don't mention it.

38:42.594 --> 38:44.034
Is Ms. Yu's faucet at home

38:44.034 --> 38:45.634
too high-tech for you?

38:45.835 --> 38:47.554
It's different from mine.

38:47.634 --> 38:48.634
I got confused.

38:48.875 --> 38:49.634
No worries.

39:03.475 --> 39:04.835
- It's alright.
- Okay, Mr. Shen.

39:19.475 --> 39:20.034
Xu Yan.

39:20.514 --> 39:22.275
Sorry. The traffic was terrible.

39:27.114 --> 39:28.874
Mr. Shen, nice to meet you.

39:28.874 --> 39:30.835
I'm Zhou Zeyuan, Xu Yan's friend.

39:32.674 --> 39:33.360
Hello.

39:34.034 --> 39:35.074
Are you dining here too?

39:35.355 --> 39:36.594
Didn't Xu Yan inform you?

39:36.755 --> 39:37.875
She invited me here.

39:46.875 --> 39:47.915
I've been swamped

39:47.955 --> 39:48.955
and forgot to tell you.

39:49.808 --> 39:50.640
It's okay.

39:51.355 --> 39:52.275
She said you'd be

39:52.275 --> 39:53.395
having lunch here.

39:53.674 --> 39:55.795
- So she invited me over.
- Okay.

39:56.194 --> 39:57.594
Mr. Shen, the dishes are ready.

39:58.915 --> 40:00.395
- An extra table setting.
- Yes, sir.

